FROM node:16-buster-slim AS builder

WORKDIR /relay
RUN mkdir /relay/.lnd
COPY --chown=1000:1000 . .

RUN apt-get update

RUN apt install --no-install-recommends -y make python3-minimal
RUN which python3
RUN apt install --no-install-recommends -y g++ gcc libmcrypt-dev
RUN apt-get -y --no-install-recommends install git

RUN rm ./package-lock.json

RUN npm install

RUN cp /relay/config/app.json /relay/dist/config/app.json
RUN cp /relay/config/config.json /relay/dist/config/config.json

RUN chown -R 1000:1000 /relay

FROM node:16-buster-slim

USER root

RUN apt-get update
RUN apt-get -y --no-install-recommends install git

USER 1000

WORKDIR /relay

COPY --from=builder /relay .

EXPOSE 3300

ENV NODE_ENV production
ENV NODE_SCHEME http
ENV PORT 3300

CMD [ "node", "/relay/dist/app.js" ]
